OL,3,CCulture Secretary asks BBC to see if
OL,4,Cit can recoup money from Huw Edwards
OL,6,FThe Culture Secretary has asked the
OL,7,FBBC to look into whether it can recoup
OL,8,Fmoney from Huw Edwards' pay packet
OL,9,Fafter the former broadcaster admitted
OL,10,Faccessing indecent images of children.
OL,12,FLisa Nandy spoke with BBC director
OL,13,Fgeneral Tim Davie on Thursday after
OL,14,FEdwards admitted making indecent
OL,15,Fphotographs, with seven of the 41
OL,16,Fimages being of the most serious type.
