OL,6,FMr Davie has defended his decision to
OL,7,Femploy the veteran broadcaster until
OL,8,FApril, five months after he was told
OL,9,Fof Edwards' arrest in November over
OL,10,Fthe most serious category of indecent
OL,11,Fimages of children.
