OL,3,CCulture Secretary asks BBC to see if
OL,4,Cit can recoup money from Huw Edwards
OL,6,FAfter the meeting between Ms Nandy and
OL,7,FMr Davie, a statement issued by the
OL,8,FDepartment for Culture, Media and
OL,9,FSport said: "The Culture Secretary is,
OL,10,Flike the whole nation, shocked by Huw
OL,11,FEdwards' abhorrent actions, and her
OL,12,Fthoughts are with the victims whose
OL,13,Flives have been destroyed. It is now
OL,14,Ffor the judiciary to decide on an
OL,15,Fappropriate sentence.
