OL,6,FBefore Edwards resigned on medical
OL,7,Fadvice, he was the broadcaster's
OL,8,Fhighest-paid newsreader, with a pay
OL,9,Fbracket between #475,000 and #479,999
OL,10,Ffor the year 2023/24, according to the
OL,11,FBBC's latest annual report.
OL,13,FIt marked a #40,000 pay rise from 2022/
OL,14,F23, when he was paid between #435,000
OL,15,Fand #439,999.
