OL,6,FThe DCMS statement added that Ms Nandy
OL,7,F"sought assurance that the BBC has
OL,8,Frobust processes in place regarding
OL,9,Fnon-editorial complaints, and the
OL,10,Fhandling of complex contractual
OL,11,Fmatters, so that in future it can act
OL,12,Fat pace and be transparent with the
OL,13,Fpublic at the earliest opportunity to
OL,14,Fensure trust is maintained".
OL,16,FMs Nandy has asked the broadcaster to
OL,17,Fkeep her updated on any developments
OL,18,Fin the case.
