OL,6,FIn an interview with BBC News on
OL,7,FThursday, the director general
OL,8,Fdefended the rise, saying it was made
OL,9,Fup of an "inflationary increase" and
OL,10,Fwork Edwards did at the BBC in
OL,11,FFebruary 2023 before any allegations
OL,12,Fwere made.
OL,14,FMr Davie also said the corporation
OL,15,Fwill "look at all options" in trying
OL,16,Fto reclaim pay from Edwards after the
OL,17,Frevelations.
OL,19,FThe BBC chief said: "These are,
OL,20,Funfortunately, the specifics of how it
OL,21,Fworks, that we can't claw back pension.
