OL,10,FAsked how much BBC managers were told
OL,11,Fin November after Edwards' arrest, Mr
OL,12,FDavie said: "We knew it was serious,
OL,13,Fwe knew no specifics, apart from the
OL,14,Fcategory of the potential offences."
OL,16,FHe also confirmed that the chief
OL,17,Fexecutive of BBC News & Current
OL,18,FAffairs, Deborah Turness, knew about
OL,19,Fthe charges before this week, BBC News
