OL,6,FMr Davie defended the corporation's
OL,7,Fdecision not to sack Edwards in
OL,8,FNovember, saying: "The police came to
OL,9,Fus and said, 'Look, we need to do our
OL,10,Fwork in total confidence, we've
OL,11,Farrested, please keep this
OL,12,Fconfidential'.
OL,14,F"And at that point, I think the
OL,15,Fprinciple is clear in my mind, and I
OL,16,Fsay we thought long and hard about
OL,17,Fthis, this wasn't a knee-jerk decision.
